de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces

Interface IWelcomePanelCreator


  • public interface IWelcomePanelCreator
    This interface generalizes the creation of TaksPanes on the WelcomePanel. The WelcomePanel has three rows which can be filled a TaskPanel. Beside the default ones, You are able to configure them in the mediatrix.properties with welcomepanel.implementor.i where i is the row number. The value is the implementing class, default, or empty.
    Author:
    andi
